text: The Rohrbach District is a district in the state of Upper Austria in Austria. The district has 40 municipalities: * Afiesl * Ahorn * Aigen-Schlägl * Altenfelden * Arnreit * Atzesberg * Auberg * Haslach an der Mühl * Helfenberg * Hofkirchen im Mühlkreis * Hörbich * Julbach * Kirchberg ob der Donau; There is no new mayor yet (as of the last week of October 2024).https://today.rtl.lu/news/world/a/2244922.html.
